### Get all groups
GET http://localhost:8080/api/groups
Accept: application/json

###

### Get a group by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/groups/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new group
POST http://localhost:8080/api/groups
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My Test Group",
  "description": "This is a new group"
}

###

### Update a group
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/groups/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Group",
  "description": "This group has been updated"
}

###

### Delete a group
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/groups/1

### Get a group by user id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/groups/user/1
Accept: application/json

